column6: At Matsu'o's estate, Psylocke discovers things are not as they seem. X-Men ally Yukio is at the scene, prepared to stop Pyslocke from carrying out her mission. And a stranger on his own hunt for Matsuo'o detonates the estate with explosive flame.
